<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q1_v10" title="Q1_v10" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Se considera la expresión <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>. Un estudiante afirma: 'El valor de la expresión es <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math>'. ¿Cuál de las siguientes alternativas describe correctamente esta situación?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">La afirmación del estudiante es correcta.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al calcular <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math> y luego <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, la afirmación “el valor es 10” no es correcta.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">La afirmación del estudiante es incorrecta, porque el valor de la expresión es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Primero, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>. Luego, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Finalmente, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>. La afirmación del estudiante es incorrecta y esta alternativa la describe correctamente.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">La afirmación del estudiante es incorrecta, porque el valor de la expresión es <m:math><m:mn>26</m:mn></m:math>.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El cálculo correcto es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>, después <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y finalmente <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, el valor no es <m:math><m:mn>26</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">La afirmación del estudiante es incorrecta, porque el valor de la expresión es <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math>.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al resolver la expresión se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>, luego <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y por eso <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>. En consecuencia, el valor no es <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Resolver el paréntesis</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Primero se calcula <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Multiplicar los dos factores</strong></p>
            <p>Ahora la expresión queda:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Como el producto de dos números negativos es positivo:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Restar el resultado obtenido</strong></p>
            <p>Se reemplaza la multiplicación por <m:math><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El valor de la expresión es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, la afirmación del estudiante “el valor de la expresión es <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math>” es incorrecta.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>